name: lexicographicallyPrecedes(_:by:)
desc: Returns a Boolean value indicating whether the sequence precedes another sequence in a lexicographical (dictionary) ordering, using the given predicate to compare elements.
declaration: func lexicographicallyPrecedes<OtherSequence>(_ other: OtherSequence, by areInIncreasingOrder: (Range<IndexSet.Element>, Range<IndexSet.Element>) throws -> Bool) rethrows -> Bool where OtherSequence : Sequence, Range<IndexSet.Element> == OtherSequence.Element
